citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4:10-4:43 pm
on 05/20/2015.
The inspector rang the doorbell and called two phone numbers and left messages.
